d at the time of\ninhibition. We test features of motif patterns by using regression models for\nboth individual patterns and their combination and we find that motifs as\nfeatures are better predictors of the future network organization than\nindividual node centralities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 3 Mar 2019 08:43:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-05"}
